<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Eberhard von Bachenstein</head><p>Der Rat teilt Unkenntnis von einer Fehdeerklärung des N. Fürsich, Diener der Stadt, mit, bittet Eberhard jedoch um Herausgabe beschlagnahmten Garns und von Hühnern Nürnberger Bürger.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_390" id="194v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_390_r1l16"><expan>Eb<ex>erhart</ex></expan> von Pachenſtein </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_390_r1l17">Lıeber <expan>Eb<ex>erhart</ex></expan> Als Jr vns <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt vvie ew der ~ fürſıch </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_390_r1l18">vnſer dıener gen vns verſagt <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> ſüll / Da vviſſen vvir </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_390_r1l19">
<del rend="strikethrough">nih </del> nıht / daʒ Er ew ichts gen vns verſagt hab / Doch ſo </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_390_r1l20"><expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vvir Jn beſant vnd <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> brief hören laſſen / vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_390_r1l21">Er ſpricht / Jn <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> etlich <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>burge<ex>r</ex></expan> cʒu ew geſant </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_390_r1l22">von garn vnd hüner wegen / die Jr Jn <expan>genome<ex>n</ex></expan> habt </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_390_r1l23"><expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> Als Jr vns nu ſchreibt / <expan>vven<ex>n</ex></expan> Jr den <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> ıre garn </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_390_r1l24">vvıderſchıckt / So vviſſen vvir nichts daʒ vvir mit ew </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_390_r1l26">cʒeſchıcken <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> lıeb vnd gut / <expan>dat<ex>um</ex></expan> <expan>fe<ex>ri</ex>a</expan> ıııj̃ <expan>p<ex>oſt</ex></expan> Lucie </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_390" id="194v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan>Eb<ex>erhart</ex></expan> von Pachenstein </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab>Lieber <expan>Eb<ex>erhart</ex></expan>, als ir uns
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>schr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt, wie ew der
                        Fürsich, unser diener, gen uns versagt <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> süll,
                        da wissen wir niht, daz er ew ichts gen uns versagt hab, doch so
                                <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir in besant und
                            <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> brief hören lassen und er spricht, in
                                <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> etlich <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>burge<ex>r</ex></expan> czu ew gesant von garn und hüner wegen, die
                        ir in <expan>genome<ex>n</ex></expan> habt; <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> als
                        ir uns nu schreibt, <expan>wen<ex>n</ex></expan> ir den
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> ire garn widerschickt, so wissen wir
                        nichts, daz wir mit ew cze schicken <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>,
                                <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> lieb und gut.
                            <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>fe<ex>ri</ex>a</expan> iiii <expan>p<ex>ost</ex></expan> Lucie.</ab>
</div>
</div></body>
